name: Super Bubble Remix
overview: A shareware Bubble Ghost clone. SUPER BUBBLE REMIX was included on the coverdisk CD of Amiga Format #123. A game featuring 32 colours graphics in a vertical overscan screen, more than 10 songs and jingles, 40 levels with varied puzzles and traps, bonus display features, high score table with saving option, 50/60Hz support and at the end you get a nice end game sequence.
